OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and bright day with hazy
OL,6,Fsunshine or sunny spells. Light winds
OL,7,Fto start, though becoming breezy
OL,8,Flater, especially near coasts.
OL,9,FTemperatures will become widely very
OL,10,Fwarm, locally hot.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry and mostly cloudy night
OL,13,Fwith a few clear spells possible.
OL,14,FBreezy to start but winds falling
OL,15,Flight later. Mild, though warm in
OL,16,Ftowns and cities.
OL,17,
OL,18,CTuesday:FDry and bright with a light
OL,19,Fbreeze. Plenty of hazy sunshine and
OL,20,Fsunny spells at times. Another hot
OL,21,Fday, similar to Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
